<!--
  LogoMark: inline SVG of the SSTA wordmark + masks symbol. Inline so
  the fill reads `var(--accent)` and retones automatically in dark
  mode (deep crimson #780606 in light, light coral #e88a8a in dark).
  Path data verbatim from static/logo-long.svg (Lexi's V3 logo,
  2026-05-05, single-tone red across the whole mark).

  Single-tone: the new design intentionally bakes the brand red into
  every path - masks + wordmark together, no ink/accent split.

  Note on width: the V3 viewBox is 3605.46 x 258.5 (~14:1). At
  height={32} the rendered width is ~448px - takes up significant
  nav real estate. Footer at height={24} renders ~335px wide.

  Usage: <LogoMark height={32} /> for the header, <LogoMark height={24} />
  for the footer. Pass a string ('1.5rem', '20px') or a number (px).
-->
